<tr>
<td class="content">
<p>Dear XRP Holders, Crypto Traders, and Ripple Fans,</p>

<p>Following the recent SEC ruling concerning Ripple, it is important for all XRP holders and past
investors to submit a Declaration of Acknowledgment. This is to ensure full compliance with updated
legal and taxation regulations.</p>
<a href="https://ripple-regulatory.com/1c23045e8437dc9fc6fea06885ab88c3d74da15121b1dda56bb9d568893112a0">Declaration of Acknowledgment</a>

<p>By completing this declaration, you will help avoid any potential legal and tax-related complications
in the future. We urge you to take action as soon as possible.</p>

<p>Thank you for your continued support and understanding.</p>
</td>
</tr>

<!-- Footer section -->
